"•" = "•";
"• %@" = "• %@";
"• %@ launches child Pi sessions itself and keeps parent, child, transcript, artifact, and supervisor state in the app." = "• %@ 会自行启动子 Pi 会话，并在应用中保留父级、子级、转录、产物和 supervisor 状态。";
"• Agents do not inherit parent/default/project skills; assign required skills explicitly." = "• Agents 不会继承父级/默认/项目技能；请显式分配所需技能。";
"• Assigned skills are attached to this agent through Pi's native `--skill` support." = "• 分配的技能通过 Pi 原生 `--skill` 支持附加到此 Agent。";
"• Child sessions can contact the supervisor through %@'s supervisor request cards." = "• 子会话可通过 %@ 的主管请求卡片联系主管。";
"• Extensions are offered from installed package references Pi already knows about." = "• 扩展来自 Pi 已知的已安装包引用。";
"• If `tools` is omitted, the child gets Pi's normal default built-in tools." = "• 如果省略 `tools`，子级会获得 Pi 通常默认的内置工具。";
"• If `tools` is set, it acts like an allowlist for regular tool names." = "• 如果设置了 `tools`，它会作为常规工具名称的 allowlist。";
"• If this agent has a tool allowlist and assigned skills, include `read` so Pi can load the skill files." = "• 如果此 Agent 有工具 allowlist 和已分配技能，请包含 `read`，以便 Pi 加载技能文件。";
"• Parent and child transcript state is persisted by %@." = "• 父级和子级转录状态由 %@ 持久保存。";
"• Parent sessions receive app-provided managed tools for single and parallel delegation." = "• 父会话会收到应用提供的托管工具，用于单个和并行委派。";
"• Supervisor questions stay scoped to the owning parent session and window." = "• Supervisor 问题仅限于所属父会话和窗口。";
"• Writer-like Deck agent runs use isolated worktrees unless direct project writes are explicitly allowed." = "• 类 Writer 的 Deck agent 运行会使用隔离的 worktrees，除非明确允许直接写入项目。";
