"Confirm actions:" = "确认操作：";
"Ask before committing or pushing" = "提交或推送前先询问";
"On by default. Turn off to run Commit and Commit & Push immediately from the toolbar." = "默认开启。关闭后，工具栏会立即执行 Commit 和 Commit & Push。";
"Uses your Pi default model unless you pick a cheaper, faster one here. Apple Foundation Model runs locally; other models use a hidden no-thinking Pi helper session." = "除非在这里选择更便宜、更快的模型，否则使用 Pi 默认模型。Apple Foundation Model 本地运行；其他模型使用隐藏的无思考 Pi 助手会话。";
"Worktree isolation:" = "Worktree 隔离：";
"Run each new session in its own git branch + worktree" = "为每个新会话创建独立 git 分支和 worktree";
"Off by default. When enabled, every new session creates a branch named agent-deck/session-<id> and an isolated working copy under ~/Library/Application Support/agent-deck/Session Worktrees/. Use the Merge toolbar button to bring the work back into the source branch. Only affects new sessions; existing sessions stay in the project root." = "默认关闭。启用后，每个新会话会创建名为 agent-deck/session-<id> 的分支，并在 ~/Library/Application Support/agent-deck/Session Worktrees/ 下创建隔离工作副本。使用 Merge 工具栏按钮将工作合回源分支。仅影响新会话；现有会话仍在项目根目录中运行。";
"Keep after merge:" = "合并后保留：";
"Keep worktree and branch after a successful merge" = "成功合并后保留 worktree 和分支";
"On by default. A successful Merge lands the work on the source branch and preserves the session worktree and branch so you can keep iterating and merge again later. Turn off if you'd rather have the worktree removed and the branch deleted as soon as it's merged. Deleting a session from the list always removes its worktree regardless of this setting. Only matters when Worktree isolation is on." = "默认开启。成功 Merge 会把工作合入源分支，并保留会话 worktree 和分支，便于继续迭代并再次合并。如果希望合并后立即移除 worktree 并删除分支，可关闭此项。从列表删除会话始终会移除对应 worktree。仅在 Worktree 隔离开启时生效。";
